      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Honing Your Hunting Horn",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nHarmonize with the sounds of\r\nnature as you serenade these\r\nmonster to permanent sleep\r\nand you\u0027re sure to find a new\r\ntune for the hunting horn!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Manier la corne de chasse",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique ! Apprends \u00E0 ne\r\nfaire qu\u0027un avec la nature tout en\r\nber\u00E7ant les monstres jusqu\u0027au repos\r\n\u00E9ternel, et tu d\u00E9couvriras de\r\nnouvelles m\u00E9lodies pour ta corne\r\nde chasse en un rien de temps !",
